{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"requestProgress","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The state and progress of an inactive or completed pack are computed lazily. If"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you need the state or progress of a pack whose "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"type":"text","text":" property is currently"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"set to "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackState\/MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", observe KVO change notifications on this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"pack’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"type":"text","text":" key path, then call this method. Alternatively, you can add an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"observer for "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" about this pack that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"come from the default notification center."}]}]}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Request an asynchronous update to the pack’s "},{"code":"state","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"progress","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" properties."}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/requestProgress"},"metadata":{"title":"requestProgress","fragments":[